# Routing

**Fonte:** `.ai/rules/10-routing.md`

## Feature routes
- `loadChildren` — nunca `component` directo para features
- `title` na rota
- Export: `FEATURE_ROUTES` ou `FEATURE_ROUTES: Routes`

## Rotas protegidas
- `canActivate: [authGuard]` — rotas autenticadas
- `canActivate: [authGuard, roleGuard]` + `data: { requiredPermission: 'x.read' }` — RBAC

Exemplo: @src/app/features/users/users.routes.ts

## Registo em app.routes.ts
- Dentro do shell (children)
- `loadChildren: () => import('./features/{feature}/{feature}.routes').then(m => m.FEATURE_ROUTES)`
